videos.description: Ole Miss advances to the Sweet 16 for the first time since 2007 with win against No. 1 Stanford.

videos.headline: Coach 'Yo' gets emotional following Ole Miss' win vs. Stanford
videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Yolett McPhee-McCuin gets emotional after her team's historic win against top-seeded Stanford.

videos.headline: Emotional Coach Yo expresses joy over Ole Miss win
videos.description: After the Rebels upset 1-seed Stanford on the road to advance to the Sweet 16, Yolett McPhee-McCuin says, "This is for all the people with a dollar and a dream."

videos.headline: What went wrong for Stanford in upset loss to Ole Miss?
videos.description: Monica McNutt lays out how Ole Miss was able to attack Stanford's weaknesses in a stunning upset in the Round of 32.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Analysis (What went wrong for Stanford in upset loss to Ole Miss?) 2023/3/19 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: 8-seed Rebels score stunning upset of 1-seed Stanford
videos.description: Relying on a gritty defense to build an early advantage, Ole Miss holds on to edge the Cardinal on the road, 54-49, in a second-round NCAA Tournament thriller.
